            "DisplayOrder": 450,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 4370,
            "LocalizeKR": "물론, 세상 모든 것이……",
            "LocalizeJP": "もちろん、\n世の中のすべてが――",
